• Any other purpose authorized under Permissible Purposes of Consumer
Reports subsection.
(2) Exclusions on Term "Consumer Report"
Except as provided in paragraph Restriction on Sharing of Medical Information,
the term "consumer report" does not include:
• Any report contains information solely about transactions or experiences
between the consumer and the person making the report.
• Any communication of that information among persons related by common
ownership or affiliated by corporate control.
• Any communication of other information among persons related by common
ownership or affiliated by corporate control, if it is clearly and
conspicuously disclosed to the consumer that the information may be
communicated among such persons and the consumer is given the
opportunity, before the time that the information is initially communicated,
to direct that such information not be communicated among such persons.
