tolerances can't exceed 8%, except for simplifying compliance with irregular
payments.
(e) Authorization of Tolerances in Determining Annual Percentage
Rates
For creditors calculating the annual percentage rate differently from subsection (d),
the Bureau may allow other reasonable tolerances.
