Transactions], 1640 [Civil Liability], and 1666e [Written Notice by Obligor to
Creditor Under Correction of Billing Errors] of this title, this subchapter and the
regulations issued thereunder do not affect the validity or enforceability of any
contract or obligation under State or Federal law.
