(a) In General
Notwithstanding any other provision of law, whenever a servicer of residential
mortgages agrees to enter into a qualified loss mitigation plan with respect to 1 or
more residential mortgages originated before May 20, 2009, including mortgages
held in a securitization or other investment vehicle:

