Section 1639b: Residential Mortgage Loan
Origination
(a) Finding and Purpose
(1) Finding
The Congress finds that economic stabilization would be enhanced by the
protection, limitation, and regulation of the terms of residential mortgage credit
and the practices related to such credit, while ensuring that responsible, affordable
mortgage credit remains available to consumers.
(2) Purpose

